Helpful app, the only concern I have, is when the archers score app, is going to run on android? I've been waiting for this for quite a long time, and I miss it being on my iPhone. It's very helpful scoring app, that I really enjoyed using. I would give it a 5 star rating...

This is a great app, with fantastic support. Was having an issue (one I created) emailed them with my question and problems I was having had a response and solution and explanation within the same day which was a sunday. Well worth the money and easy to use with good instructions and good user interface. It has shortened the time it takes me to get my sight marks from about 8 hour/200 arrows to about 20min/30 arrows. Buy it and don't look back you won't regret it
